<td>
<p><span class="date">Oct. 7, 1975</span>, <a href="/rio/citation/Pub._L._94-106" old_href="/us/pl/94/106/s812" refid="94-106" type="pl">Pub. L. 94–106, § 812</a>, <a href="/rio/citation/89_Stat._540" old_href="/us/stat/89/540" refid="89-540" type="stat">89 Stat. 540</a>.</p>
