<div class="note" topic="miscellaneous"><span class="heading centered smallCaps">Transfer of Responsibilities and Functions Relating to Electromagnetic Spectrum Operations</span>
<p><a href="/rio/citation/Pub._L._116-283">Pub. L. 116–283, div. A, title I, § 152</a>, <span class="date" date="2021-01-01">Jan. 1, 2021</span>, <a href="/rio/citation/134_Stat._3440">134 Stat. 3440</a>, as amended by <a href="/rio/citation/Pub._L._117-81">Pub. L. 117–81, div. A, title IX, § 907(c)(1)</a>, <span class="date" date="2021-12-27">Dec. 27, 2021</span>, <a href="/rio/citation/135_Stat._1875">135 Stat. 1875</a>, which authorized the <span link="https://liicornell.org/liifedent/dod_osd_secretary_of_defense" occur="23" src="named_federal_agencies">Secretary of Defense</span> to transfer the responsibilities and functions of the Commander of the<a aria-label="Definitions -  United States " class="colorbox-load definedterm" href="/definitions/uscode.php?width=840&amp;height=800&amp;iframe=true&amp;def_id=10-USC-2032517217-397636830&amp;term_occur=999&amp;term_src="> United States </a>Strategic Command relating to electromagnetic spectrum operations, was transferred to <a href="/rio/citation/Pub._L._115-232">section 1053 of Pub. L. 115–232</a>, set out as a note below, and redesignated as subsec. (g) of that section by <a href="/rio/citation/Pub._L._117-81">Pub. L. 117–81, div. A, title IX, § 907(c)(2)</a>, <span class="date" date="2021-12-27">Dec. 27, 2021</span>, <a href="/rio/citation/135_Stat._1875">135 Stat. 1875</a>.</p>
