</div>
<div class="subparagraph indent2"><span class="num" value="D">“(D)</span>
<div class="content"> a detailed comparison of funds obligated for the Initiative during the previous fiscal year to the amount of funds requested for such fiscal year.</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="subsection indent0"><span class="num" value="g">“(g)</span><span class="heading"> Briefings Required.—</span>
