<p><a href="/rio/citation/Pub._L._112-239">Pub. L. 112–239, div. A, title X, § 1061(a)</a>, (b), <span class="date" date="2013-01-02">Jan. 2, 2013</span>, <a href="/rio/citation/126_Stat._1939">126 Stat. 1939</a>, directed the <span link="https://liicornell.org/liifedent/dod_osd_secretary_of_defense" occur="159" src="named_federal_agencies">Secretary of Defense</span> to review and update guidance related to electronic warfare and directed the Commander of the<a aria-label="Definitions -  United States " class="colorbox-load definedterm" href="/definitions/uscode.php?width=840&amp;height=800&amp;iframe=true&amp;def_id=10-USC-2032517217-397636830&amp;term_occur=999&amp;term_src="> United States </a>Strategic Command to update and issue guidance regarding the responsibilities of the Command with regard to joint electronic warfare capabilities.</p>
