<div class="note" topic="miscellaneous"><span class="heading centered smallCaps">Program To Commemorate 60th Anniversary of World War II</span>
<p><a href="/rio/citation/Pub._L._108-375">Pub. L. 108–375, div. A, title X, § 1032</a>, <span class="date" date="2004-10-28">Oct. 28, 2004</span>, <a href="/rio/citation/118_Stat._2045">118 Stat. 2045</a>, authorized the <span link="https://liicornell.org/liifedent/dod_osd_secretary_of_defense" occur="242" src="named_federal_agencies">Secretary of Defense</span> to conduct a program during fiscal year 2005 to commemorate the 60th anniversary of World War II.</p>
