<div class="note" topic="miscellaneous"><span class="heading centered smallCaps">Annual Report on the Conduct of Military Operations Conducted as Part of Operation Enduring Freedom</span>
<p><a href="/rio/citation/Pub._L._107-314">Pub. L. 107–314, div. A, title X, § 1043</a>, <span class="date" date="2002-12-02">Dec. 2, 2002</span>, <a href="/rio/citation/116_Stat._2646">116 Stat. 2646</a>, required annual reports on the conduct of military operations conducted as part of Operation Enduring Freedom, starting <span class="date" date="2003-06-15">June 15, 2003</span>, and ending no later than 180 days after the date of the cessation of hostilities undertaken as part of Operation Enduring Freedom.</p>
