<div class="note" topic="miscellaneous"><span class="heading centered smallCaps">Defense Reform Initiative Enterprise Pilot Program for Military <span link="https://liicornell.org/liifedent/dod_manpower" markup="no-show" occur="2" src="named_federal_agencies">Manpower</span> and Personnel Information</span>
<p><a href="/rio/citation/Pub._L._106-65">Pub. L. 106–65, div. A, title IX, § 924</a>, <span class="date" date="1999-10-05">Oct. 5, 1999</span>, <a href="/rio/citation/113_Stat._726">113 Stat. 726</a>, authorized the <span link="https://liicornell.org/liifedent/dod_osd_secretary_of_defense" occur="281" src="named_federal_agencies">Secretary of Defense</span> to designate the Secretary of the Navy as the <span link="https://liicornell.org/liifedent/department_of_defense" occur="214" src="named_federal_agencies">Department of Defense</span> executive agent for carrying out the pilot program described in <a href="/rio/citation/Pub._L._105-262">Pub. L. 105–262, § 8147</a>.</p>
