<div class="note" topic="miscellaneous"><span class="heading centered smallCaps">Report Concerning Appropriate Forum for Judicial Review of <span link="https://liicornell.org/liifedent/department_of_defense" markup="no-show" occur="228" src="named_federal_agencies">Department of Defense</span> Personnel Actions</span>
