<div class="subsection indent0"><span class="num" value="b">“(b)</span>
<div class="content"> The Secretary shall ensure that a disbursement in excess of the threshold amount applicable under section (a) is not divided into multiple disbursements of less than that amount for the purpose of avoiding the applicability of such section to that disbursement.”</div>
</div>
